comment:
* Indicates errors that may be generated during initialization by the
     * middleware. They are applicable to both streaming and file-download use-cases.

variables.name: ERROR_DUPLICATE_INITIALIZE
variables.comment:
* Indicates that the app tried to create more than one instance each of
         * {@link MbmsStreamingSession} or {@link android.telephony.MbmsDownloadSession}.

variables.name: ERROR_APP_PERMISSIONS_NOT_GRANTED
variables.comment: Indicates that the app is not authorized to access media via MBMS.

variables.name: ERROR_UNABLE_TO_INITIALIZE
variables.comment: Indicates that the middleware was unable to initialize for this app.
